Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:36.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Tentar te machucar com palavras cruéis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:42.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Mesmo que o mundo inteiro não acredite em você
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:47.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}E coloque uma coroa de espinhos em sua cabeça
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:53.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}eu posso estar do seu lado, e só o seu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:59.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Eu conheço a sua dor e solidão
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}Então, tudo que me completa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:08.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,580)\3c&H000000&}eu vou te dar isso agora
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:48.48,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Eu{\3c&H000000&}sou{\3c&H000000&}um{\3c&H000000&}navegador
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:16.01,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&}Nee, kono sekai ni wa takusan no shiawase ga aru nda yo, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:22.64,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}{\3c&H000000&}Itsuka futari de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:30.73,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&}D{\3c&H000000&}a{\3c&H000000&}r{\3c&H000000&}e{\3c&H000000&}k{\3c&H000000&}a{\3c&H000000&} {\3c&H000000&}g{\3c&H000000&}a{\3c&H000000&} {\3c&H000000&}k{\3c&H000000&}i{\3c&H000000&}m{\3c&H000000&}i{\3c&H000000&} {\3c&H000000&}n{\3c&H000000&}o{\3c&H000000&} {\3c&H000000&}k{\3c&H000000&}o{\3c&H000000&}t{\3c&H000000&}o{\3c&H000000&} {\3c&H000000&}w{\3c&H000000&}o{\3c&H000000&} {\3c&H000000&}u{\3c&H000000&}s{\3c&H000000&}o{\3c&H000000&}t{\3c&H000000&}suki to yonde
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:36.36,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}kokoronai kotoba de kizutsuke you toshite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:42.16,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Sekai ga kimi wo shinjiyou to shinakute mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:47.92,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Ibara no kanmuri wo noseyo to shite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:53.67,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}watashi wa kimi dake no mikata ni nareru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:59.14,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Sono kodoku itami wo watashi wa shitteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:08.90,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,580)\3c&H000000&}Eu dedicarei isso a você
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.53,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...o vento passou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:10:01.74,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Os dois se sobrepuseram{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:10.88,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu cantarei a prova de que você viveu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:23.56,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pelo bem daqueles que não têm nomes{\i0}
